      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "For the Bureau's information a Mrs. [REDACTED] of Saybrook, Illinois reported to this office the finding of a flying disc in her front yard at 6:00 A.M. on July 26, 1947.",
