      "lineId": "page_0052-l0014",
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "It appears from investigation conducted by an Agent of this office that the stability of [REDACTED] is questionable. However the alleged flying disc was obtained and it is apparently the concoction of some of the juveniles in the area. It is an old wooden platter, which has assembled on it a silver plate, a spark plug, a timer, and some old brass tubing. Photographs were taken of the same and there are six views enclosed herewith.",
